quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  15,37,"Allâh said: "
  15,38,""
  15,39,"[Iblîs (Satan)] said: "
  16,16,"And landmarks (signposts during the day) and by the stars (during the night), they (mankind) guide themselves."
  16,17,"Is then He, Who creates as one who creates not? Will you not then remember?"
  16,18,"And if you would count the favours of Allâh, never could you be able to count them. Truly! Allâh is Oft-Forgiving, Most Merciful."